AUDIO: 'So everything is looking pretty good. So one last thing before we go, um sometimes when you build these environments out in the final application, the environment will begin to clip um ran- unexpectedly and randomly. So in order to fix that, we'

[17:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'want to select our our environment and then we want to come to this first NGC 3D GS component and we want to scroll down search for bounds.'

[17:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Now now we have bound scale. Th- this is what\'s controlling the clipping uh when our environment clips in and out. So we want to if if you\'re experiencing unexpected clipping in your built application, you just need to come and'

[17:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
